name: InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
comment: This is the exception for invalid or inappropriate algorithm parameters.

constructors.name: InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
constructors.comment:
Constructs an InvalidAlgorithmParameterException with no detail
 message.
 A detail message is a String that describes this particular
 exception.

constructors.name: InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
constructors.comment:
Constructs an InvalidAlgorithmParameterException with the specified
 detail message.
 A detail message is a String that describes this
 particular exception.

constructors.name: InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
constructors.comment:
Creates a {@code InvalidAlgorithmParameterException} with the
 specified detail message and cause.

constructors.name: InvalidAlgorithmParameterException
constructors.comment:
Creates a {@code InvalidAlgorithmParameterException} with the
 specified cause and a detail message of
 {@code (cause==null ? null : cause.toString())}
 (which typically contains the class and detail message of
 {@code cause}).
